{"id":243639,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-安徽访民呼吁社会关注年近七旬的夏培勤/","date":"2012-07-29T10:16:27Z","modified":"2012-07-29T10:16:27Z","title":"维权网 | 安徽访民呼吁社会关注年近七旬的夏培勤劳教案（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span> </span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><br /><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员周维林报道）安徽多位访民向本网信息员提供材料，呼吁社会各界关注安庆市孤寡老人夏培勤（女）因赴北京最高法院申诉而被安庆市劳动教养委员会决定劳动教养一年案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据访民称，夏培勤老人是因为不服安徽省高级法院（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>）皖民申字第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0543</span><span>号民事裁定书向最高人民法院申诉，却被公安抓捕，安庆市劳动教养委员会宜劳教字【</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>】第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>号《劳动教养决定书》称，夏培勤于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">31</span><span>日</span><span>分别被以扰乱公共场所秩序被行政拘留十日；该委员会审核认定：“夏培勤在其信访事项终结的情况下，仍与杨爱芬、江光宝等人串联，商量在全国两会期间赴京上访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>，夏培勤与杨爱芬等八人携带上访材料欲前往天安门地区上访，被北京公安局民警查获。”以此，安庆市劳动教养委员会</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>会议决定对夏培勤劳动教养一年，执行期限自</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>止。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>夏培勤老人则于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>提起行政复议，其复议要点有五：一、安庆市劳动教养委员会对其劳教没有夏培勤违法的证据予以支持；二、安庆市公安机关对其两次拘留皆无证据支持，其中</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>的拘留没有送达行政处罚决定书；三、夏培勤身份证上出生于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1944</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月，实际生于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1939</span><span>年，且身体多病，早已失去劳动能力，依法怎能予以劳动教养强制其劳动？四、其于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>向最高法院申诉，约定两个月接访一次，而《劳动教养决定书》中称其“在其信访事项终结的情况下仍与杨爱芬、江光宝等人串联，商量在全国两会期间……”与事实不符；五、程序违法，没有告知其亲属她的违法事由、关押时间、地点。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>访民对本网信息员强调，夏培勤老人年已七旬，身体多病，毫无劳动能力，劳教本身没有任何的法律支持，地方政府可以随意对访民或他们稳控的对象实施劳动教养，这是一种严重侵犯人权的行为。鉴于夏培勤老人孤寡一人，无近亲属，故希望社会各界予以关注，使老人早日获释。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-fGLLP-mV2lc/UBUCES4lk6I/AAAAAAAAKJc/Wx9FONIxyUs/s1600/P1020469.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-fGLLP-mV2lc/UBUCES4lk6I/AAAAAAAAKJc/Wx9FONIxyUs/s320/P1020469.JPG\" width=\"215\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-X91j4qUR_ag/UBUCILqrsBI/AAAAAAAAKJk/H7XGAoGjBGg/s1600/P1020470.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-X91j4qUR_ag/UBUCILqrsBI/AAAAAAAAKJk/H7XGAoGjBGg/s320/P1020470.JPG\" width=\"233\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-SEP0fXmBocs/UBUCKMpicBI/AAAAAAAAKJs/BDgZlyxGPrE/s1600/P1020472.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-SEP0fXmBocs/UBUCKMpicBI/AAAAAAAAKJs/BDgZlyxGPrE/s320/P1020472.JPG\" width=\"224\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-wrP7eCBO0Lw/UBUCMuv4v0I/AAAAAAAAKJ0/9ngOZXSk69k/s1600/P1020473.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-wrP7eCBO0Lw/UBUCMuv4v0I/AAAAAAAAKJ0/9ngOZXSk69k/s320/P1020473.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-rbPUWY3QoXg/UBUCPv-cB6I/AAAAAAAAKJ8/rFss30yp7os/s1600/P1020474.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-rbPUWY3QoXg/UBUCPv-cB6I/AAAAAAAAKJ8/rFss30yp7os/s320/P1020474.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-6143838516417529786?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}